# Skeleton

The IDS and QBDS team plan to deprecate the QBDS repo and most of its components in the upcoming fiscal year (2026). At that point, QBDS components will continue to exist but will no longer be maintained. If you have an existing usage of this component in your repo under the `@qbds` namespace, we recommend migrating to the `@ids-ts` version.

If you have any bug fixes or new features you'd like to report or contribute, please post in the [#ask-ids](https://intuit.enterprise.slack.com/archives/C53V5U3S5) Slack channel so that we can help coordinate your work between both namespaces.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/skeleton
```

```tsx
import {
  Skeleton,
  SkeletonContainer,
  SkeletonText,
  SkeletonIcon,
  SkeletonChip,
  SkeletonAction,
} from '@ids-ts/skeleton';
```

